metadata.name: STRIVING TOGETHER
metadata.description:
STRIVING TOGETHER 

In life, in order to achieve, one needs to strive. 
The determination in your face, the strength in your sinews, the tenacity of your back, the shown-veins of your forceful arms, the firmness of your resolve, focused, all prove to idea that failure will never overtake you when you strive enough.
Strive forward
Strive together!
